=== 立法 ===
[[File:Rep._Jody_Hice_and_Lila_Rose.png|缩略图]]一同呼籲結束對美國計劃生育聯盟的納稅人資助。]]
生命行動反對[[聯邦政府|聯邦政府]]和州政府資助[[美國計劃生育聯盟|美國計劃生育聯盟]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Pro-life movement urges Congress to defund Planned Parenthood immediately|url=https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2017/sep/5/pro-life-movement-urges-defund-planned-parenthood/|accessdate=2021-01-10|date=2017-09-05|publisher=Washington Times|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112025351/https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2017/sep/5/pro-life-movement-urges-defund-planned-parenthood/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Planned Parenthood reports record-high abortions, taxpayer funding amid battles with Republicans|url=https://www.foxnews.com/politics/planned-parenthood-record-abortions-government-funding|accessdate=2021-01-10|date=2020-01-07|last=Dorman|first=Sam|work=Fox News|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325075651/https://www.foxnews.com/politics/planned-parenthood-record-abortions-government-funding|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2011年，在生命行動發布了有關計劃生育的秘密影片後，[[美國眾議院|美國眾議院]]於2011年2月通過了[[共和黨_(美國)|共和黨]]眾議員[[麥克·彭斯|麥克·彭斯]]的一項修正案，以削減聯邦政府對美國計劃生育聯盟的資助<ref>{{Cite web|title=House defunds Planned Parenthood|url=https://www.politico.com/story/2011/02/house-defunds-planned-parenthood-049830|accessdate=2021-01-10|date=2011-02-18|last=Nocera|first=Kate|publisher=POLITICO|language=en|archive-date=2015-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150806004102/http://www.politico.com/news/stories/0211/49830.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 社群媒體 ===
生命行動曾遭到多個[[社群媒體|社群媒體]]平台的限制<ref>{{Cite web|title=TikTok restores pro-life group's account, blames 'human error' for ban|url=https://www.christianpost.com/news/tiktok-reinstates-live-action-pro-life-group-blames-human-error-for-ban.html|accessdate=2021-01-10|date=2020-02-02|publisher=Christian Post|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809165937/https://www.christianpost.com/news/tiktok-reinstates-live-action-pro-life-group-blames-human-error-for-ban.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2017年，[[推特|推特]]禁止生命行動在其平台上投放廣告<ref>{{Cite news|title=Yes, Twitter can reject this anti-abortion group’s ads for displaying ‘sensitive content’|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/business/economy/twitter-wont-run-an-anti-abortion-groups-paid-advertising-unless-it-scrubs-its-website-of-sensitive-content/2017/09/22/d914fc8a-9ecb-11e7-9083-fbfddf6804c2_story.html|newspaper=Washington Post|date=2017-09-22|accessdate=2021-01-10|language=en-US|first=Tracy|last=Jan|archive-date=2021-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109094346/https://www.washingtonpost.com/business/economy/twitter-wont-run-an-anti-abortion-groups-paid-advertising-unless-it-scrubs-its-website-of-sensitive-content/2017/09/22/d914fc8a-9ecb-11e7-9083-fbfddf6804c2_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年6月，[[Pinterest|Pinterest]]永久禁止了生命行動，並將生命行動的網站列入禁止的色情網站黑名單<ref>{{Cite web|title=Pinterest Has Banned The Influential Anti-Abortion Group Live Action After First Classifying It As Porn|url=https://www.buzzfeednews.com/article/briannasacks/pinterest-bans-live-action|accessdate=2021-01-10|date=2019-06-11|publisher=BuzzFeed News|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208122944/https://www.buzzfeednews.com/article/briannasacks/pinterest-bans-live-action|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年8月，生命行動向Pinterest和[[YouTube|YouTube]]發出了[[停止並終止|停終信函]]，指稱這兩個平台正在壓制生命行動的內容<ref>{{Cite web|title=Pro-Life Group Sends Cease-and-Desist Letters to YouTube, Pinterest Alleging Censorship|url=https://www.nationalreview.com/news/pro-life-group-alleges-censorship-by-youtube-pinterest/|accessdate=2021-01-10|date=2019-09-06|work=National Review|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226230141/https://www.nationalreview.com/news/pro-life-group-alleges-censorship-by-youtube-pinterest/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2019年8月，[[臉書|臉書]][[事實查核|事實查核]]人員將生命行動的兩支影片標記為「虛假」<ref>{{Cite web|title=Group slams Facebook and fact-checker, threatens lawsuit over ‘false’ rating of abortion claim|url=https://www.foxnews.com/tech/pro-life-facebook-fact-checker-lawsuit-abortion-false|accessdate=2021-01-10|date=2019-08-30|last=Berger|first=Judson|work=Fox News|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210209025519/https://www.foxnews.com/tech/pro-life-facebook-fact-checker-lawsuit-abortion-false|dead-url=no}}</ref>，此一舉動受到[[約什·霍利|約什·霍利]]和[[泰德·克魯茲|泰德·克魯茲]]等共和黨參議員的批評，最終臉書撤回了生命行動影片中的標記<ref>{{Cite web|title=Facebook removes fact check from anti-abortion video after criticism|url=https://thehill.com/policy/technology/461092-facebook-removes-fact-check-from-anti-abortion-video-after-criticism|accessdate=2021-01-10|date=2019-09-12|last=Conradis|first=Brandon|work=TheHill|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111194228/https://thehill.com/policy/technology/461092-facebook-removes-fact-check-from-anti-abortion-video-after-criticism|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年1月30日，[[TikTok|TikTok]]以「多次違反社群規則」為由封禁了生命行動的帳號。次日，TikTok恢復了生命行動的帳號，並稱之前的封禁是「人為錯誤」<ref>{{Cite web|title=TikTok Reinstates Pro-Life Org Live Action, Says Initial Ban for ‘Multiple Community Guidelines Violations’ Was ‘Result of a Human Error’ [Updated]|url=https://www.nationalreview.com/news/tiktok-bans-pro-life-org-live-action-for-unspecified-multiple-community-guidelines-violations/|accessdate=2021-01-10|date=2020-01-31|work=National Review|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201207221631/https://www.nationalreview.com/news/tiktok-bans-pro-life-org-live-action-for-unspecified-multiple-community-guidelines-violations/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 示威 ===
2019年5月，生命行動成員在[[費城|費城]]示威，抗議[[賓夕法尼亞州眾議院|賓夕法尼亞州眾議院]]議員{{le|布萊恩·西姆斯|Brian Sims}}此前騷擾反墮胎人士的行為<ref>{{Cite web|title=‘We Will Not Back Down To Bullies’: Anti-Abortion Rally Outside Philadelphia Planned Parenthood Draws Large Crowd|url=https://philadelphia.cbslocal.com/2019/05/10/planned-parenthood-live-action-philadelphia-brian-sims-rally/|accessdate=2021-01-10|date=2019-05-10|publisher=CBS Philadelphia|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190512095208/https://philadelphia.cbslocal.com/2019/05/10/planned-parenthood-live-action-philadelphia-brian-sims-rally/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

